part.text: We met this year since we were in the same class. At first I thought u were kinda cute and you seemed cool but I thought you didn't like me because when I tried to talk it just seemed like I bothered u😅 so I left it alone. We talk about anything under the sun from marvel to what we want to do, to random stuff like why our pets eat their vomit. What I like abt u isn't just that I think ur cute bc looks aren't everything I care more for personality. So the fact that you strive to do the best at anything and everything you do is good, your athletic, your actually Christian which is hard to find and though you may struggle you're constantly working on ur relationship with him, you like to listen to people and aren't afraid yo speak your mind or speak up for urself and others, and your pretty chill.
